    AuthPayload
    Specifies a full auth flow payload, representing a completed or in-progress identity and authorization/consent flow, performed by a machine on behalf of an end user.

    Specifies a full auth flow payload, representing a completed or in-progress identity and authorization/consent flow, performed by a machine on behalf of an end user.

    Specifies an authorization token, in the OAuth2 access_token format.
